詹妮弗·哈德森 (Jennifer Hudson) 宣布发行 10 年来首张专辑《The Gift Of Love》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/jennifer-hudson-releasing-debut-holiday-album-the-gift-of-love-first-in-10-years-3791898?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=珍妮弗·哈德森发行首张假日专辑《爱的礼物》，十年来首张Kyann-Sian WilliamsTue, 17 Sep 2024 16:14:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsR&BSoul https://www.nme.com/?p=3791898 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·哈德森 (Jennifer Hudson) 在 2024 年托尼奖颁奖典礼上。图片来源：Dimitrios Kabouris/Getty Images for Tony Awards Productions" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张节日唱片收录了她与现任男友 Common 合作的一首歌</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jennifer-hudson-releasing-debut-holiday-album-the-gift-of-love-first-in-10-years-3791898">詹妮弗·哈德森 (Jennifer Hudson) 发布 10 年来首张专辑《The Gift Of Love》的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="詹妮弗·哈德森 (Jennifer Hudson) 在 2024 年托尼奖颁奖典礼上。图片来源：Dimitrios Kabouris/Getty Images for Tony Awards Productions" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/jennifer-hudson-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/jennifer-hudson">詹妮弗·哈德森 (Jennifer Hudson)</a>透露，她的首张假日专辑《The Gift Of Love》将于今年秋天发行，这也是她 10 年来的首次发行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/respect-review-aretha-franklin-3014519">“尊重”评论：艾瑞莎·富兰克林传记片充满了心灵和灵魂</a></strong></li></ul><p>哈德森证实她最近与 Interscope Records 签署了一份新协议后发布了这一消息。 《The Gift Of Love》将是她在该厂牌下发行的第一张专辑，也是她 2014 年第三张录音室专辑《JHUD》的后续专辑。</p><p>这位 EGOT 获胜者在她的社交媒体上公布了这件艺术品的记录。她在预告片中调侃说“假期季节从今年十月开始”，展示了她装饰一棵圣诞树的样子。她在标题中写道：“爱的礼物 [心形表情符号] 我的第一张假日专辑将于 10 月 18 日发行！ [10 月 18 日]。</p><p> “<a href="https://jenniferhudson.lnk.to/TheGiftofLove" target="_blank" rel="noopener">立即通过我的简介中的链接进行预订</a>。我等不及它成为你的了！ #爱的礼物。”</p><p>粉丝们可以听到哈德森对标志性圣诞歌曲《铃儿响叮当》深情演绎的片段，该歌曲将出现在专辑中。看看下面的预告片。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_k5rMwxkLt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; fle